-- David Beckham Has Given a Verbal Agreement to Join PSG, Le Parisien Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2011-12-21T06:06:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/david-beckham-has-given-a-verbal-agreement-to-join-psg-le-parisien-says.html
David Beckham  has given verbal
agreement to joining Paris Saint-Germain and is likely to sign
an 18-month playing contract in coming days, French daily
newspaper Le Parisien reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Beckham will be paid a gross monthly salary of 800,000
euros, ($1.05 million) according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  